 $Id: CalendarBuilder.java,v 1.36 2009/03/05 06:11:54 fortuna Exp $

 Created: Apr 5, 2004
Parses and builds an iCalendar model from an input stream. Note that this class is not thread-safe.

Version:
2.0

Ben Fortuna
